 The two bots stopped. They could not lead him to the base. He was not a very 
good stealth bot was he? or maybe his ego was so big it blinds his 
senjudgment. Savior powered up his shields and Gabriel pulled his sowrd of 
faith. (saviors main weapon is that his shields gather the energy fired on 
him and shoots it back. like optimus primal in beast machines.) Savior flew 
behind the bot while Gabriel shot at him with his wrist guns. Savior flew up 
full speed from behind and attempted to put him in a full nelson lock to 
block and defence of the bots against gabriels shots.
